__Usage__
Normal RFID operation only requires local EEPROM database. Management for this database provided by CLI interface available through USB or wired ethernet.

Other functions operate on a strictly http-client basis. 
*) Open-Door latch override setting periodically checked from HTTP.
*) RFID entry log buffer is periodically uploaded through HTTP.

*) RFID credential database periodically uploaded through HTTP.

*) RFID credential database periodically checked for new entries from HTTP.
*) RFID credential database periodically checked for revoked entries from HTTP.

*) Occupancy sensor status change leads to immediate update through HTTP get request.
*) Sensor values periodically uploaded through HTTP.

